---
title: Herby Asparagus and Tomato Bake with Israeli Couscous, Thyme, and Feta
description: As they burst in the oven, tomatoes create their own flavorful sauce. Served on a bed of toothsome Israeli couscous, this dish tastes like a slow-cooked masterpiece. Only you’ll know how quick it was!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56f032aaf8b25e1f338b4567.jpg
